snippet.title: Hot Wheels Unleashed: Batman Expansion | DC Kids FanDome | DC Kids
snippet.description:
Hot Wheels Unleashed is a brand new action-packed arcade-style racing game! Here's your first look at the upcoming Batman Expansion that allows you to explore and race through the mysterious Batcave!

Welcome to DC Kids FanDome, an epic global Livestream event where DC Kids showcases its biggest movies, games, shows, comics, and more! See your favorite DC characters, check out super-exclusive sneak peeks, and meet the heroes who make it all happen!

DC Kids is home to all your favorite DC characters, videos, comics, games, and activities from Teen Titans Go!, DC Super Hero Girls, Batman Unlimited, Justice League of America, and more!
 
#DCKids #KidsCartoons #DCKidsFandome
